Package: doctorRbite
Title: An updated R Markdown thesis template using the bookdown package
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Chester", "Ismay", email = "chester.ismay@gmail.com", role = "cre"),
    person("Nick", "Solomon", email = "nick@nicksolomon.me", role = "aut"),
    person("Vivek", "Bhardwaj", email = "vivbhr@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: Using the bookdown package and LaTeX and Word thesis templates from
    Uni Freiburg (faculty of biology), this package aims to encourage reproducible research using
    simple Markdown syntax while embedding all of the R code to produce plots
    and analyses as well.
Maintainer: Vivek Bhardwaj <vivbhr@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0),
    devtools,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    bookdown,
    knitr
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 1.18) - http://pandoc.org
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
